<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 00:50:13 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>汇丰成本难题加剧投资者银行审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-cost-conundrum-intensifies-investor-bank-scrutiny-2024-02-22/</link><description>汇丰银行成本不断攀升，加剧了投资者对大银行如何管理开支的担忧，使高管面临着迅速解决支出问题的压力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 00:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-cost-conundrum-intensifies-investor-bank-scrutiny-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国2023年煤电审批量增加，气候目标面临风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/china-2023-coal-power-approvals-rose-putting-climate-targets-risk-2024-02-22/</link><description>周四的研究显示，中国将在 2023 年再批准 114 吉瓦 (GW) 的煤电装机容量，较上年增长 10%，在批准了数十座新电厂后，这个世界最大的碳污染国家现在面临着无法实现气候目标的风险。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 00:05:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/climate-energy/china-2023-coal-power-approvals-rose-putting-climate-targets-risk-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>美国国会议员中国委员会主席抵达台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmaker-who-chairs-china-committee-arrives-taiwan-2024-02-22/</link><description>众议院中国问题特别委员会主席、美国众议员迈克·加拉格尔周四与其他议员组成的代表团抵达台湾，并将会见台湾总统和当选总统。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 00:04:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-lawmaker-who-chairs-china-committee-arrives-taiwan-2024-02-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国脱钩加速，台湾芯片公司涌向日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chip-firms-flock-japan-china-decoupling-accelerates-2024-02-21/</link><description>随着越来越多的台湾芯片公司在这里扩张，日本重建半导体行业的努力正受到强心剂——不仅是为了支持台积电的新工厂，而且还对日本半导体行业的前景感到兴奋。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 23:02:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/taiwan-chip-firms-flock-japan-china-decoupling-accelerates-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>《红茶》导演告诉柏林电影节，世界存在于以欧洲为中心的视野之外</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/world-exists-beyond-eurocentric-gaze-black-tea-director-tells-berlinale-2024-02-21/</link><description>对于导演阿卜杜勒拉赫曼·西萨科 (Abderrahmane Sissako) 来说，在他的两洲茶迷爱情片《红茶》中展现非洲在大银幕上不常见的一面非常重要，该片于周三晚上在柏林电影节上首映。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 22:03:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/lifestyle/world-exists-beyond-eurocentric-gaze-black-tea-director-tells-berlinale-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：英伟达定下基调</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-21/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 21:47:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>第一量子矿业宣布资本重组以减少债务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-says-it-is-seeking-20-billion-over-panama-mine-closure-order-2024-02-21/</link><description>第一量子矿业周三宣布了一系列资本重组措施，以加强其资产负债表并削减债务，此举将帮助这家加拿大矿业公司实现其“运营目标”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:50:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/first-quantum-says-it-is-seeking-20-billion-over-panama-mine-closure-order-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>罗纳尔多进球，阿尔纳赛尔确认亚冠联赛取得进展</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-lopes-penalty-moves-marinos-into-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-21/</link><description>克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多 (Cristiano Ronaldo) 的阿尔纳赛尔 (Al-Nassr) 周三晋级亚洲冠军联赛四分之一决赛，这支总部位于利雅得的球队以 2-0 击败沙特职业联赛球队阿尔法哈 (Al-Fayha)，以总比分 3-0 获胜。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 14:26:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/late-lopes-penalty-moves-marinos-into-asian-champions-league-quarters-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>世贸组织推动改革重重障碍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/world-trade-organizations-push-reform-plagued-by-obstacles-2024-02-21/</link><description>在贸易保护主义抬头​​的时代，世界贸易组织可能会决定其在制定全球商业规则方面的未来角色，而就在谈判召开前几天，世界贸易组织却陷入了如何处理其“不举行会议”的困境。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 13:13:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/world-trade-organizations-push-reform-plagued-by-obstacles-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>独家：继华为Mate 60 Pro之后，美国瞄准中国顶级芯片制造厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-top-chipmaking-plant-after-huawei-mate-60-pro-sources-say-2024-02-21/</link><description>三名知情人士表示，拜登政府正在加大对中国最大受制裁芯片制造商的压力，在该公司为华为 Mate 60 Pro 手机生产先进芯片后，切断了该公司最先进的工厂从美国进口的产品。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 12:09:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-targets-chinas-top-chipmaking-plant-after-huawei-mate-60-pro-sources-say-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>通过库里的收购，中国的京东可能会获得欧洲扩张的捷径</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/with-currys-buyout-chinas-jdcom-could-get-hungered-short-cut-europe-expansion-2024-02-21/</link><description>如果京东确实收购了英国电子零售商 Currys，中国电子商务巨头京东将以低廉的价格获得在英国和欧洲快速扩张所需的商店和仓库网络。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:19:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/with-currys-buyout-chinas-jdcom-could-get-hungered-short-cut-europe-expansion-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：英伟达在美联储会议纪要通过期间获利了结</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-21/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 11:07:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>中印两军就边界问题举行“建设性”会晤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-indian-militaries-hold-constructive-meeting-border-issues-ministry-2024-02-21/</link><description>中国国防部在一份声明中表示，中印两军周一就解决边界问题举行了建设性会议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-indian-militaries-hold-constructive-meeting-border-issues-ministry-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>安全部门称俄罗斯是对北约抱有希望的瑞典最大的安全威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-is-biggest-security-threat-nato-hopeful-sweden-security-service-says-2024-02-21/</link><description>瑞典安全部门周三表示，俄罗斯是瑞典面临的主要国际安全威胁，外国敌人可能会试图利用伊斯兰主义者和极右翼分子实施极端主义暴力的较高风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 10:26:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russia-is-biggest-security-threat-nato-hopeful-sweden-security-service-says-2024-02-21/</guid></item><item><title>红海弹道导弹袭击引发亚洲对防御的兴趣</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</link><description>专家和行业官员表示，在红海使用反舰弹道导弹（ASBM）激发了亚洲对用于击落反舰弹道导弹的系统的兴趣，尽管中国拥有庞大的反舰弹道导弹武库，构成了更严峻的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 21 Feb 2024 09:39:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/red-sea-ballistic-missile-attacks-trigger-asian-interest-defences-2024-02-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>